Package: normalmultinomial
Type: Package
Title: Normal-Multinomial Distribution
Version: 0.2.2
Author: Marc Comas Cuf\\u00ed <marc.comas@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Marc Comas Cuf\\u00ed <marc.comas@gmail.com>
Description: A colletion of tools to simulate samples from a Normal-Multinomial distribution and to
    to fit the parameters to a given counting sample by maximum likelihood estimation using
    montecarlo approaches.
License: GPL
